Game class
----------

This event operates on an instance of the [game class](Game_class "Game class") type {{{gameclass}}}

Description
-----------

Returns a random targeted entity.

Usage
-----

*entity* randomTarget( *string* ignoreName )

Parameters
----------

-   [ignoreName] - The name of an entity to ignore.

Examples
--------

    Â 
    $my_entity.randomTarget("player");

Notes
-----

This script event returns a random targeted entity as an entity.

Pass an entity name as ignoreName to skip that entity.

